<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">

<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8" />
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0" />
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="/stylesheets/output.css" />
    <link rel="shortcut icon" href="/images/logo/logo.ico" type="image/x-icon" />

    <script src="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/gsap@3.12.5/dist/gsap.min.js" defer></script>
    <script src="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/gsap@3.12.5/dist/ScrollTrigger.min.js" defer></script>
    <script src="https://unpkg.com/lenis@1.1.13/dist/lenis.min.js" defer></script>
    <script type="module" src="/js/animations.js" defer></script>

    <title>OnlyFiles</title>
</head>

<body class="overflow-x-hidden bg-gradient-to-br from-white to-blue-100">
    <%- include("header") %>
    <div class="container mx-auto px-4">

        <div class="hero-trigger">
            <div class="hero mt-52 mb-40 sm:mt-64 sm:mb-56 flex flex-col items-center">
                <h1 class="font-bold text-4xl md:text-6xl text-center">Store your files online</h1>
                <a href="<%= locals.currentUser ? "drive" : "register" %>" class="m-4 px-8 py-2 border-2 text-blue-500 border-blue-500 rounded-xl font-bold hover:bg-blue-500 hover:text-white transition duration-200">
                    <%= locals.currentUser ? "Open Drive" : "Get started" %>
                </a>
            </div>
        </div>

        <div class="arrow-trigger flex flex-col justify-center items-center animate-bounce">
            <h2 class="arrow text-blue-500">How it works</h2>
            <svg class="arrow h-16 w-16 fill-blue-500" height="800px" width="800px" version="1.1" id="Layer_1" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" xmlns:xlink="http://www.w3.org/1999/xlink" viewBox="0 0 330 330" xml:space="preserve">
                <g id="XMLID_169_">
                    <path id="XMLID_197_" d="M304.394,139.394l-139.39,139.393L25.607,139.393c-5.857-5.857-15.355-5.858-21.213,0.001
                    c-5.858,5.858-5.858,15.355,0,21.213l150.004,150c2.813,2.813,6.628,4.393,10.606,4.393s7.794-1.581,10.606-4.394l149.996-150
		            c5.858-5.858,5.858-15.355,0-21.213C319.749,133.536,310.251,133.535,304.394,139.394z" />
                    <path id="XMLID_221_" d="M154.398,190.607c2.813,2.813,6.628,4.393,10.606,4.393s7.794-1.581,10.606-4.394l149.996-150
		            c5.858-5.858,5.858-15.355,0-21.213c-5.857-5.858-15.355-5.858-21.213,0l-139.39,139.393L25.607,19.393
		            c-5.857-5.858-15.355-5.858-21.213,0c-5.858,5.858-5.858,15.355,0,21.213L154.398,190.607z" />
                </g>
            </svg>
        </div>

        <div class="mx-0 sm:mx-8 lg:mx-24 my-96 flex flex-col gap-96 font-bold text-2xl md:text-4xl lg:text-5xl xl:text-6xl">

            <div class="node-express-trigger">
                <div class="node-express flex items-center">
                    <div class="max-w-40 sm:max-w-60 md:max-w-72 lg:max-w-80 xl:max-w-96">
                        <img src="/images/intro/node.webp" alt="" class="p-8">
                        <img src="/images/intro/express.webp" alt="" class="p-8">
                    </div>
                    <h1>App manages server-side operations with Node.js and Express</h1>
                </div>
            </div>

            <div class="passport-trigger">
                <div class="passport flex items-center">
                    <img src="/images/intro/passport.webp" alt="" class="max-w-40 sm:max-w-60 md:max-w-72 lg:max-w-80 xl:max-w-96 p-8">
                    <h1>Passport.js is used to handle user authentication and sessions</h1>
                </div>
            </div>

            <div class="supabase-trigger">
                <div class="supabase flex items-center">
                    <img src="/images/intro/supabase.webp" alt="" class="max-w-40 sm:max-w-60 md:max-w-72 lg:max-w-80 xl:max-w-96 p-8">
                    <h1>Supabase Storage is used for uploading files</h1>
                </div>
            </div>

            <div class="postgre-trigger">
                <div class="postgre flex items-center">
                    <img src="/images/intro/postgre.webp" alt="" class="max-w-40 sm:max-w-60 md:max-w-72 lg:max-w-80 xl:max-w-96 p-8">
                    <h1>Application utilizes PostgreSQL as its database to efficiently store and manage user data, folders and files</h1>
                </div>
            </div>

            <div class="prisma-trigger">
                <div class="prisma flex items-center">
                    <img src="/images/intro/prisma.webp" alt="" class="max-w-40 sm:max-w-60 md:max-w-72 lg:max-w-80 xl:max-w-96 p-8">
                    <h1>Prisma is used as an ORM for interacting with database</h1>
                </div>
            </div>

            <div class="tailwind-trigger">
                <div class="tailwind flex items-center">
                    <img src="/images/intro/tailwind.webp" alt="" class="max-w-40 sm:max-w-60 md:max-w-72 lg:max-w-80 xl:max-w-96 p-8">
                    <h1>Tailwind CSS for rapid and responsive styling</h1>
                </div>
            </div>

            <div class="gsap-trigger">
                <div class="gsap flex items-center">
                    <img src="/images/intro/gsap.webp" alt="" class="max-w-40 sm:max-w-60 md:max-w-72 lg:max-w-80 xl:max-w-96 p-8">
                    <h1>And finally all these animations were made with GSAP</h1>
                </div>
            </div>

        </div>

    </div>
</body>

</html>